{"tid":158592,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"搵工搵到好茫(5)","createTime":"2017-03-16T11:27:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-16T11:28:26.000Z","uid":76563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6ae67cbc5b6e9001345e3ce476c223b2f195e39b","tid":158592,"uid":76563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T11:27:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n其實本身都係打算考正苦文職<br />\n只係今年失敗咗開始搵工<br />\n嚟緊會搵吓有無啲輕鬆文職比自己進修<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果我當年 25 歲迷失個陣 ,  有連登既話<br />\n我應該考 ACO / CA 就算 <br />\n總好過我依家發展成死局一個。<br />\n<br />\n如果你心目中有邊份政府 / 公營機構想做,  就應該搵一份有相關工作性質既工,  人工反而係其次。</blockquote><br />\n巴打你宜家咩景況<br />\n我見你平時有投資開 已經好過我"},{"pid":"5fbb2960f67184ae8e9c80f49559f5d2709780e6","tid":158592,"uid":76563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T11:28:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/158591/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/158591/page/1</a><br />\n已經有人開咗..."}]}